PERCY Tau might not be famous for his dance moves, but that does not mean he can't break it down when he wants to. He recently showed that he is just as competent on the dance floor as he is on the football pitch. The 24-year-old was seen showing off to his Club Brugge teammates a few dance moves associated with Amapiano music in Mzansi. It is safe to say, Tau won the dressing room dance contest with some of his teammates impressed.   